        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10959"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Anmol.Magic - Out of This World Canada Tour"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Experience an unforgettable evening with <b>Anmol.Magic</b>, one of Canada's most captivating mentalists and illusionists, as he brings his acclaimed <b>Out of This World Canada Tour</b> to Prince Edward Island.</p>\n\n<p> Blending mind-reading, impossible illusions, audience participation, and unforgettable moments of wonder, this live theatrical experience will leave you questioning what is truly possible. Whether you're coming with family, friends, or for a unique night out, this is a show designed to amaze audiences of all ages.</p>\n\n<p>Prepare for an interactive evening filled with mystery, laughter, and jaw-dropping moments that you'll be talking about long after the curtain falls.</p>\n\n<p><b>Duration:</b> Approximately 2 hours (No Intermission)</p>\n\n<p><b>Recommended Audience:</b> Suitable for ages 2+</p>\n\n"
      }
    ],
