        "@value": "CARSON FULLERTON BAND"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Since the age of 3, Carson Fullerton has been an on-stage performer like no other. Now, at the age of 9 years old, Carson has already taken his guitar and mandolin to Nashville to record his first cover song, has \nshared the stage with many well-known local talents, and has opened up for big acts like Tim Hicks, Jimmy Rankin and Classified. Come see him live at your Osprey on October 10!</p>\n\n<style>\n    .titleTax {\n       display: none !important;\n   }\n</style>\n\n"
      }
