    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Drag Bingo - Hosted by Brooke Rivers & Trinity Foxx"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Drag Bingo Night is coming to Glasgow Square for an unforgettable evening of laughter, excitement, and fabulous entertainment!</p>\n\n<p>Hosted by the dynamic duo Brooke Rivers and Trinity Foxx, this high-energy event combines all the fun of a classic bingo hall with the glamour and humour of drag performance. Grab your bingo cards and get ready to play for an incredible lineup of prizes, including cash, gift cards, and tickets to upcoming Glasgow Square performances.</p>\n\n<p>Whether you're a seasoned bingo pro or just looking for a fun night out with friends, Drag Bingo Night promises great entertainment, plenty of surprises, and chances to win throughout the evening. </p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
