        "@value": "Elton Songs: The Elton John Experience"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The tribute band Elton Songs invites you to experience Elton John's greatest hits. Featuring remarkably faithful vocal imitations, meticulous staging, and iconic costumes, the show draws inspiration from the flamboyant style of the 70s and 80s, paying tribute to the British star's universe and creating the illusion of being in the presence of the legendary Sir Elton John. </p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
