        "@id": "https://tproatlantic.ticketpro.ca/api/v1/resources/1695193855.jpeg?version=1"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/genid/1370e92ae0d98a59"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10937"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10937"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Montuno Cubano: Cuban Soul, Maritime Spirit"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Imagine the passion, energy, and irresistible rhythms that draw visitors from around the world to\nCuba's vibrant music scene—now brought to life right here in Prince Edward Island. This special\nconcert offers a rare opportunity to experience the magic of authentic Cuban music without\ntravelling to Cuba.</p> \n<p>Featuring the internationally acclaimed musicians, Montuno Cubano, alongside talented\nMaritime guest artists, this unique performance celebrates both the rich musical traditions of\nCuba and the beloved songs of Atlantic Canada. Throughout the evening, audiences will enjoy\nperformances by Montuno Cubano, Maritime artists showcasing East Coast favourites, and\nexciting collaborative numbers that bring all the musicians together on one stage.</p> \n<p>The concert will move between the soulful sounds and infectious rhythms of Cuba, the\ncherished melodies and stories of the Maritimes, and dynamic collaborations that highlight the\nconnections between these musical worlds. Together, the artists will demonstrate how different\nmusical traditions can create something fresh, inspiring, and unforgettable.</p> \n<p>More than just a concert, this is a rare musical encounter where Cuban soul and Maritime spirit\nmeet, celebrating the universal language of music in an experience unlike anything audiences\nhave seen before.</p> \n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
