    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10905"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Relive the Music - 50s 60s & 70s SHOW "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b><a href='https://relivethemusic.ca/' target='_blank'>'RELIVE THE MUSIC'</a></b> is finally back and now even better as we've cranked it up a notch by adding the biggest hits of <b>70s ROCK, DISCO & FUNK</b>. We still keep the biggest, most popular hits of the 50s & 60s, but have added our favourite 70s Artists. </p>\n\n<p>There is a reason we have had over 170 consecutive standing ovations across Canada and the USA to date.  It's like watching over two dozen Tribute Shows in one evening. Over 30 Costume changes.  You will hear songs by Bill Haley & His Comets, Paul Anka, Chordettes,  Dean Martin, Dores Day,  Elvis,  Harry Balafonte, Patsy Cline, Frank Sinatra, The Platters, Connie Francis, The Ronettes, The Beatles, Jerry Lee Lewis, Danny & the Juniors, Little Richard, James Brown, Check Berry, Dion DiMucci, Sam Cooke, Chubby Checker,  Beach Boys, Four Seasons, The Supremes, Aretha Franklin, Rolling Stones, Steppenwolf, Led Zeppelin, Nancy Sinatra, Sonny & Cher, Neil Diamond, Gloria Gaynor, Lipps Inc, Donna Summer, the Tramps, Eagles, Queen, Abba, Bee Gees, Tina Turner and more...</p>\n\n<p>A one-of-a-kind show that takes the audience through Music History, Trivia & Memories of the 50s & 60s, and the 70s Rock, Disco & Funk Era. You will likely learn many things you never knew about these artists. You will see an energetic live band, amazing front singers, and dancers transforming and reliving three decades of music, costumes, trends, and dance, with video imagery in the background.  World Champion Luisa Marshall, who has appeared twice on Oprah and the Ellen Show as Tina Turner, is one of the stars and producers. </p>\n\n\n<p><a href='https://relivethemusic.ca/' target='_blank'>www.RelivetheMusic.ca</a></p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/kCnFITvkO3Y?si=My5-L6j2zBJvvEYJ' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n\n\n"
      }
    ],
