        "@id": "https://ticketpro.ca/place/1288922214"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/image": [
      {
        "@id": "https://tproatlantic.ticketpro.ca/api/v1/resources/1694410001.jpeg?version=1"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/offers": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/genid/6ebe9babc91eec6c"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasDerivedFrom": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10918"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/url": [
      {
        "@id": "https://ww3.ticketpro.ca/event.php?event_id=10918"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "The Coldplay Show - Ultimate Hits Experience"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Coldplay are recognized world over as one of the most popular and influential bands of the new millennium. They have been performing for more than 25 years, selling out multiple nights in almost every venue, thrilling dedicated fans numbered in the millions.</p>\n\n<p>Coldplay has more than 41,000,000,000 (billion) streams on Spotify, and have sold more than 160 million albums and achieving one of the most-attended concert tour in history with their Music of the Spheres World Tour, which grossed $1.38 billion and sold 12.3 million tickets. They hold the record for most UK Albums Chart number ones without missing the top, and in 2021, 'My Universe' was the first song by a British group to debut atop the Billboard Hot 100. The band performed in one of the most iconic Super Bowl Halftime Shows of all-time in 2016, alongside Beyoncé and Bruno Mars.</p>\n\n<p>'The Coldplay Show' is the most authentic tribute, bringing the closest sonic and visual performance experience imaginable. This tribute concert features the biggest hits of all-time that include; Clocks, Scientist, Adventure of a Lifetime, Sky Full of Stars, Yellow, Paradise, Fix You, Something Just Like This, My Universe, Higher Power, Trouble and other recognizable chart-toppers.</p>\n\n<p>'The Coldplay Show' includes high-tech 3D visual elements bringing to life the true essence of the renowned Coldplay show, with truly professional band members who are seasoned tribute musicians, who have performed 1000's of shows at various festivals, theatres and live music venues. Lead vocalist and front man Andrew Sansone has been touring for more than 20 years as a professional musician. His world-class vocal stylings and dynamic stage presence leave audiences of all ages feeling emotional charged by a musical experience that you would expect from Coldplay front man Chris Martin, himself.</p>\n\n<p>Testimonial: <i>'It's all there...the voice, the sound, the songs and amazing visuals.' </i>- Larry Sylvain - The Port Theatre (Theatre Owner/Programming Director - Cornwall, Ontario, Canada)</p> \n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/orh71tqhVLs?si=DfkQznNqga1yryln' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
