    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "The Wonder Of It All"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Featuring playwright Mark Weatherley and his real-world spouse - PEI-native Monique Lund - as they depart on this journey together, sharing The Wonder of it All!</p>\n\n<p>Kingsley considered convincing Charmaine to marry him the greatest achievement of his life. That is, until a surprise from their past meddles with the certainty of their future. After 25 years, is it too late for them to rediscover the redemptive power of love?</p>\n\n<p>Full of humour and heart, the world premiere of the two-act version of The Wonder Of It All is a witty and touching comedy—a comic misadventure for modern lovers.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
